WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.280
I'm Jacqueline Nolis.

00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:13.100
This is my presentation how one time I made an entire e-commerce platform on Shiny.

00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:15.880
They said it couldn't be done, but I did it.

00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:17.680
What is that platform?

00:00:17.680 --> 00:00:23.160
That platform is ggirl, which is to make your ggplots in real life.

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:26.639
Some people may pronounce it ggirl, but it is officially ggirl.

00:00:26.639 --> 00:00:33.720
You can install it via remotes, and it lets you take a ggplot you've made that's beautiful

00:00:33.720 --> 00:00:36.500
that you wish existed in the physical realm.

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:41.639
You can then pay a modest fee, and very soon you will get an actual postcard delivered

00:00:41.639 --> 00:00:45.080
to a friend or family member.

00:00:45.080 --> 00:00:46.919
But it's all cool to talk about it.

00:00:46.919 --> 00:00:48.599
Let's actually see how it works instead.

00:00:48.599 --> 00:00:52.360
So I'm going to immediately switch out of PowerPoint and switch to a live demo.

